# GymPath Cursor Rules

Always read `AGENTS.md` first, then `MEMORY.md`, then the relevant file in `agent_docs/`.

## Architecture

- Python + Streamlit + SQLite MVP.
- `project.py` contains core logic and `main()`.
- `app.py` contains Streamlit UI.
- `test_project.py` tests deterministic functions from `project.py`.
- `ai_coach.py` handles AI API and fallback logic.
- `storage.py` handles SQLite if persistence grows.

## Workflow

- Plan before coding.
- Implement one feature at a time.
- Run `python -m pytest` after logic changes.
- Check Streamlit manually after UI changes.
- Update `MEMORY.md` after milestones.

## UI

GymPath should feel professional, clean, athletic, data-driven, and mobile-first. Use the local `frontend-design` standard when available.

## Safety

Do not make medical diagnosis claims. Severe, sharp, worsening, unusual, radiating pain, numbness, or loss of function should trigger stop-and-seek-professional-help guidance.

